data.description: Welcome to the Enchanted Valley Community. This cozy four bedroom home has two living spaces and a primary suite with bathroom and walk in closet.  So many improvements including; a newer heat pump, bathroom updates, fresh interior paint and an updated kitchen stove. The house sits on just over a third of an acre lot and has plenty of space for your outdoor hobbies. Backyard is fenced and has a large storage shed with 220 power. There is also a covered deck with additional outdoor storage space. Pop in and see all this property has to offer!
